<head>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 5% 10%;
            background-color: #ddd6fe;
            color: black;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 0.25rem;
        }

        .reset {
            background-color: #5b21b6;
            width: 150px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            height: 40px;
            color: #e7e7e7;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: 0.25s color;
        }

        .reset:hover {
            color: #f0abfc;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <span>Dear <%= name %></span>
    <span>We have recently got a request for creating an account.</span>
    <br />
    <span>If this was you, please click on the button below. Otherwise, you can ignore it.</span>
    <a href="<%= emailUrl %>" class="reset">Confirm Email</a>
    <br />
    If the button does not work, please paste the URL below into your browser:
    <a href="<%= emailUrl %>">
        <%= emailUrl %>
    </a>
</body>